 by judges who are scoring elements of the sporting performance, including objective or subjective measures such as technical performance or artistic impression.\n\n&nbsp;','What is this new sport that is winning the world','','publish','open','open','','what-is-this-new-sport-that-is-winning-the-world','','','2016-11-09 06:54:20','2016-11-09 06:54:20','',0,'https://raratheme.com/preview/numinous/?p=175',0,'post','',0),(177,1,'2016-11-09 06:34:05','2016-11-09 06:34:05','','basketball-95607_1280','','inherit','open','closed','','basketball-95607_1280-2','','','2018-12-11 14:06:45','2018-12-11 14:06:45','',175,'https://raratheme.com/preview/metro-magazine/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/basketball-95607_1280.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(178,1,'2016-11-09 06:45:09','2016-11-09 06:45:09','','sport','','inherit','open','closed','','sport','','','2018-12-11 14:06:45','2018-12-11 14:06:45','',175,'https://raratheme.com/preview/metro-magazine/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sport.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(179,1,'2016-11-09 06:53:38','2016-11-09 06:53:38','','sport','','inherit','open','closed','','sport-2','','','2018-12-11 14:06:45','2018-12-11 14:06:45','',175,'https://raratheme.com/preview/metro-magazine/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sport-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(180,1,'2016-11-09 06:53:43','2016-11-09 06:53:43','','surfing-1245930_1280','Surfing','inherit','open','closed','','surfing-1245930_1280','','','2018-12-11 14:06:45','2018-12-11 14:06:45','',175,'https://raratheme.com/preview/metro-magazine/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/surfing-1245930_1280.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(181,1,'2016-11-09 06:53:45','2016-11-09 06:53:45','','surfing-1622182_1280','','inherit','open','closed','','surfing-1622182_1280','','','2018-12-11 14:06:45','2018-12-11 14:06:45','',175,'https://raratheme.com/preview/metro-magazine/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/surfing-1622182_1280.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(182,1,'2016-11-09 06:53:47','2016-11-09 06:53:47','','b